                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="sa">Dānasāgara</title> is a 12<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> century <term xml:lang="sa">dharmanibandha</term> attributed to <persName xml:lang="sa">Ballālasena</persName>. It was edited in 1956 by Bhabatosh Bhattacarya on the basis of three manuscripts:
